        <UserObject label="" mermaidData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;sequenceDiagram\n    actor User\n    participant UI as Next.js UI\n    participant API as FastAPI\n    participant DB as PostgreSQL\n \n    User-&gt;&gt;UI: Nhap email + mat khau, bam Dang nhap\n    UI-&gt;&gt;API: POST /auth/login {email, password}\n    activate API\n    API-&gt;&gt;DB: SELECT profile WHERE email = ?\n    activate DB\n    DB--&gt;&gt;API: User record + hashed password\n    deactivate DB\n    API-&gt;&gt;API: bcrypt.verify(password, hash)\n    alt Dung thong tin\n        API--&gt;&gt;UI: {access_token, role}\n        UI-&gt;&gt;UI: Luu token vao localStorage\n        UI-&gt;&gt;User: Redirect sang /dashboard\n    else Sai thong tin\n        API--&gt;&gt;UI: 401 Unauthorized\n        UI-&gt;&gt;User: Hien loi \&quot;Email hoac mat khau khong dung\&quot;\n    end\n    deactivate API\n\n&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;config&quot;: null&#xa;}" id="cApR6UD8RmAvHbpSTtHe-1">
